column5: can someone tell me where to get groceries and beer in temiscaming and what the price of beer is there---------thanks!!!!
"Google" it. Temiscaming is a fairly decent size town, with large grocery stores.

Provigo... For those that are old enough and remember "Loblaws" grocery store in upstate, NY... Provigo is the same company that operated Loblaws... The have it all: Temiscaming Store:http://www.provigo.ca/LCLOnline/stor...p?storeId=2221
I have been up to Remigny, QC several times and recall seeing a Walmart Supercenter on my way west of 11 on 65. Maybe New Liskeard?
Yep,Shopped there the end of May.However,I noticed I was in Ontario,not Quebec.
